body: * Fixed hard mode buttons position on devices with certain aspect ratio

* Added spiral mode
* Fixed a bug with hard mode buttons overlap
* Fixed a bug with crash in HardModeView

* Reworked hard mode
* Moves count now increments per individual tile move
* Fix calculation of session average
* Small bugfixes
* Fixed a bug with game not pausing when statistics view is shown
* New settings to control anti-aliasing, delay between games, ingame info

* Added new trail gesture support for faster solving
* Added multi-color modes: rows, columns, fringe
* Added some new colors

* Make touches more responsible
* Add new tile appearance animations
- Fixed a bug with tile text animation
